                    "company": "Curiel Hygienic Engineering Consulting",
                    "description": "\u201cCuriel Hygienic Engineering Consulting\u201c is a one-man privately owned and operated consultancy business based in The Netherlands. Curiel Hygienic Engineering Consulting is founded in August 2015 after retirement of Roy Curiel. Roy has worked for more than 30 years with Unilever in the area of Hygienic Engineering as a Specialist Hygienic Processing giving full hygienic engineering support, hygienic consulting and services to Unilever R&D, Supply Chain, Engineering and factories globally.\n\nPlease CHECK my CHEC consultancy site: http://wp.me/p65V6M-4\n\nKey services are:\n- Hygienic Design of process lines\n- Hygienic equipment evaluation\n- Hygienic improvement of process equipment and process line\n- Cleaning and disinfection of process lines\n- Cleaning validation\n- Hygienic Building design\n- HACCP support\n- Hygiene auditing, and trouble shooting\n- Plant Hygi\u00ebne validation\n- Hygienic Supply Chain Management; this includes the hygienic movement and storage of raw materials, work-in-process inventory, and finished goods at the at the point of production\n- Training in the area of hyginic design and hygienic processing",
                    "title": "Owner",
                    "employment_type": null
                }
            ]
